{"word":"Marriage","slug":"marriage","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Marriage</b> Consanguineous:<br/> - Abraham and Sarah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=11&verse=29'>Gen 11:29</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=12&verse=13'>Gen 12:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=20&verse=3'>Gen 20:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=20&verse=16'>Gen 20:16</a> <br/> - Isaac and Rebekah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=24&verse=4'>Gen 24:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=24&verse=67'>Gen 24:67</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=28&verse=2'>Gen 28:2</a> <br/> - Jacob and his wives<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=29&verse=30'>Gen 29:30</a> <br/> - Levirate (the brother required to marry a brother's widow)<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=38&verse=8'>Gen 38:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=38&verse=11'>Gen 38:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=25&verse=10'>Deu 25:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=8&chapter=4&verse=5'>Rth 4:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=22&verse=24'>Mat 22:24</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=12&verse=23'>Mar 12:23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=20&verse=28'>Luk 20:28</a> <br/> Parents contract for their children:<br/> - Hagar selects a wife for Ishmael<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=21&verse=21'>Gen 21:21</a> <br/> - Abraham selects a wife for Isaac<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=24'>Gen 24</a> <br/> - Laban arranges for his daughters' marriage<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=29'>Gen 29</a> <br/> - Samson asks his parents to procure him a wife<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=14&verse=2'>Jdg 14:2</a> <br/> Parents' consent required in the Mosaic law<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=22&verse=17'>Exo 22:17</a><br/> Presents given to parents to secure their favor<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=24&verse=53'>Gen 24:53</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=34&verse=12'>Gen 34:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=22&verse=29'>Deu 22:29</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=18&verse=25'>1Sa 18:25</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=28&chapter=3&verse=2'>Hos 3:2</a><br/> Nuptial feasts<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=29&verse=22'>Gen 29:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=14&verse=12'>Jdg 14:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=17&chapter=2&verse=18'>Est 2:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=22&verse=12'>Mat 22:12</a><br/> Jesus present at<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=2&verse=5'>Joh 2:5</a><br/> Ceremony attested by witnesses<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=8&chapter=4&verse=11'>Rth 4:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=8&verse=3'>Isa 8:3</a><br/> Bridegroom exempt one year from military duty<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=24&verse=5'>Deu 24:5</a><br/> Bridal ornaments<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=49&verse=18'>Isa 49:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=2&verse=32'>Jer 2:32</a><br/> Bridal presents<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=24&verse=53'>Gen 24:53</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=45&verse=12'>Psa 45:12</a><br/> Herald preceded the bridegroom<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=25&verse=6'>Mat 25:6</a><br/> Wedding robes adorned with jewels<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=61&verse=10'>Isa 61:10</a><br/> Wives obtained:<br/> - By purchase<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=29&verse=20'>Gen 29:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=8&chapter=4&verse=10'>Rth 4:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=28&chapter=3&verse=2'>Hos 3:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=28&chapter=12&verse=12'>Hos 12:12</a> <br/> - By kidnapping<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=21&verse=23'>Jdg 21:23</a> <br/> Given by kings<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=17&verse=25'>1Sa 17:25</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=18&verse=17'>1Sa 18:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=18&verse=21'>1Sa 18:21</a><br/> Daughters given in, as rewards of valor<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=1&verse=12'>Jdg 1:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=17&verse=25'>1Sa 17:25</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=18&verse=27'>1Sa 18:27</a><br/> Wives taken by edict<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=17&chapter=2&verse=4'>Est 2:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=17&chapter=2&verse=14'>Est 2:14</a><br/> David gave one hundred Philistine foreskins for a wife<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=3&verse=14'>2Sa 3:14</a><br/> Wives among the Israelites must be Israelites<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=34&verse=16'>Exo 34:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=7&verse=4'>Deu 7:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=23&verse=22'>1Ch 23:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=9&verse=2'>Ezr 9:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=9&verse=12'>Ezr 9:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=10&verse=30'>Neh 10:30</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=13&verse=27'>Neh 13:27</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=39&chapter=2&verse=11'>Mal 2:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=46&chapter=7&verse=39'>1Co 7:39</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=47&chapter=6&verse=14'>2Co 6:14</a><br/> Betrothal, a quasi-marriage<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=1&verse=18'>Mat 1:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=1&verse=27'>Luk 1:27</a><br/> Betrothal made with the spirit<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=16&verse=8'>Eze 16:8</a><br/> Celibacy:<br/> - Deplored<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=11&verse=38'>Jdg 11:38</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=4&verse=1'>Isa 4:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=16&verse=9'>Jer 16:9</a> <br/> - Advised<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=46&chapter=7&verse=8'>1Co 7:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=46&chapter=7&verse=40'>1Co 7:40</a> <br/> Obligations under, inferior to duty to God<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=13&verse=10'>Deu 13:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=19&verse=29'>Mat 19:29</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=14&verse=26'>Luk 14:26</a><br/> Not binding after death<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=22&verse=30'>Mat 22:30</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=12&verse=25'>Mar 12:25</a><br/><a href='S:Bride'>Bride</a>; <a href='S:Bridegroom'>Bridegroom</a><br/> Unclassified scriptures relating to<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=2&verse=24'>Gen 2:24</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=46&chapter=6&verse=16'>1Co 6:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=22&verse=17'>Exo 22:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=49&chapter=5&verse=33'>Eph 5:33</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=18&verse=18'>Lev 18:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=22&verse=30'>Deu 22:30</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=20&verse=14'>Lev 20:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=20&verse=17'>Lev 20:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=20&verse=21'>Lev 20:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=21&verse=1'>Lev 21:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=21&verse=7'>Lev 21:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=21&verse=15'>Lev 21:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=36&verse=8'>Num 36:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=21&verse=14'>Deu 21:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=24&verse=5'>Deu 24:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=18&verse=22'>Pro 18:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=21&verse=9'>Pro 21:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=21&verse=19'>Pro 21:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=29&verse=6'>Jer 29:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=28&chapter=2&verse=20'>Hos 2:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=39&chapter=2&verse=16'>Mal 2:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=5&verse=32'>Mat 5:32</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=6&verse=18'>Mar 6:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=10&verse=12'>Mar 10:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=19&verse=9'>Mat 19:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=16&verse=18'>Luk 16:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=45&chapter=7&verse=3'>Rom 7:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=46&chapter=7&verse=40'>1Co 7:40</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=46&chapter=9&verse=5'>1Co 9:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=46&chapter=11&verse=12'>1Co 11:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=54&chapter=3&verse=2'>1Ti 3:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=54&chapter=3&verse=12'>1Ti 3:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=54&chapter=4&verse=1'>1Ti 4:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=54&chapter=4&verse=3'>1Ti 4:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=54&chapter=5&verse=14'>1Ti 5:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=58&chapter=13&verse=4'>Heb 13:4</a><br/> Figurative<br/> - Figurative<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=54&verse=5'>Isa 54:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=62&verse=5'>Isa 62:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=3&verse=14'>Jer 3:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=31&verse=32'>Jer 31:32</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=28&chapter=1&verse=2'>Hos 1:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=28&chapter=2&verse=20'>Hos 2:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=49&chapter=5&verse=32'>Eph 5:32</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=66&chapter=19&verse=9'>Rev 19:9</a> <br/> Parables from<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=22&verse=2'>Mat 22:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=25&verse=10'>Mat 25:10</a><br/><a href='S:Divorce'>Divorce</a>; <a href='S:Husband'>Husband</a>; <a href='S:Wife'>Wife</a>"}]}